scenes.description: Moona shows off her 3D room and poses for the camera, highlighting her new accessories like her ears.
Moona attempts to perform a moonwalk on her carpeted floor, humorously struggling before succeeding.
Moona interacts with viewers' superchats, which manifest as physical pink balls falling into her room.
Overwhelmed by the superchats, Moona falls down and transitions into her song performance.
Moona performs her original song 'High Tide'.
